snippet.title: Squid Game BIRTH TO DEATH in Real Life - Rebecca Zamolo
snippet.description:
Rebecca is playing squid game from birth to death. 

It all started when Rebecca Zamolo created "Someone BROKE into our House after GENDER REVEAL." Next Matt and Rebecca posted "Game Master Sent US Back to SQUID GAME SCHOOL In Real Life." Finally the Game Master Network created "ESCAPING TWIN ESCAPE ROOMS to Win Dream Warehouse." Now Rebecca must try to survive 24 hours inside of a squid game simulation.  Birth to death she Rebecca gives birth to her baby but it is instantly taken away by the squid game leader.  there is a clue hidden inside of this game and Matt and Rebecca must complete the games to win the secret.  What happens if you die and who set up this giant game in real life?  Squid game prom was awkward but you must play tug o war to win.  Either way it will be emotional to survive longer than other players.  Thanks for watching my funny entertainment mystery vlog videos in 2021!
